text: @FedExHelp so I’m getting a pkg delivered home tomorrow. I won’t be home. Sig required. Text notification sends me to delivery manager. Manager doesn’t give me any options. Don’t wanna miss the package. Vacation starts Wednesday. Don’t wanna forgo sig and leave at door.
